READ ME
=======

FFV-C : Frontflow / violet Cartesian




Ingredients
===========

BUILD		 How to compilation
CONTRIBUTORS    List of contributors
COPYING		 Copyright
LICENSE         License to apply
NEWS            Release note
README		 This file

bin/            Executable modules

doc/            Documents

doxygen/        Doxygen files
	
example/        Example files
	
src/		 Source files
   Cutlib-x.x   Cut information library
   F_CORE       f90 subroutines in ffvc
   F_VOF        VOF routines
   FB           flow base class
   FFV          ffvc class
   IP           Intrinsic problems
   PLOT3D       Plot3d routines
   PMlib-x.x    Performance measurement library
   Polylib-x.x  Polygon data management library
   Util_Combsph 



Prerequisite
============

- MPI library
- CPM library
- TextParser library
- CIO library



